title: 2020 Zed Tennis Open II – Doubles
text:
This was the first edition of the tournament.
<a href="Marta%20Kostyuk">Marta Kostyuk</a> and <a href="Kamilla%20Rakhimova">Kamilla Rakhimova</a> won the title, defeating <a href="Paula%20Kania">Paula Kania</a> and <a href="Anastasiya%20Shoshyna">Anastasiya Shoshyna</a> in the final, 6–3, 2–6, [10–6].
